Text of the CERN Open Hardware Licence v2 - Strongly Reciprocal:

1. Definitions

1.1 'Licensor' means the person or entity that grants access to and the right 
to use the Product Design Data under the terms and conditions of this Licence.

1.2 'Product Design Data' means the documents, schematics, PCB layouts, GDSII 
files, source code, and other digital assets that define the physical 
structure, logic, and manufacturing instructions of the Product.

1.3 'Product' means any physical object, hardware device, or integrated 
circuit manufactured, assembled, or synthesized based on the Product Design Data.

1.4 'Licensee' means any person or entity exercising rights under this Licence.

2. Grant of Rights

2.1 The Licensor hereby grants the Licensee a worldwide, royalty-free, 
non-exclusive, perpetual licence to use, copy, modify, communicate, and 
distribute the Product Design Data, as well as to manufacture and distribute 
Products derived from it, subject to the conditions in Section 3.

3. Reciprocal Conditions

3.1 If the Licensee makes any modifications to the Product Design Data, or 
manufactures Products based on it, any distribution of the modified Product 
Design Data or the resulting Products must be executed under the exact same 
terms of this Licence (CERN-OHL-S-2.0).

3.2 The Licensee must retain all original copyright notices, license 
identifiers, and disclaimer text within all copies or derivative variations 
of the Product Design Data.

3.3 Third-Party Exceptions: In accordance with microelectronics design 
paradigms, the requirement to open-source modifications does not extend to 
proprietary foundational macro-cells, standard cell libraries, or manufacturing 
process primitives provided natively by commercial semiconductor foundries 
(PDK tools), which are utilized to compile the open physical layout layouts.

4. Disclaimer of Warranty & Liability

4.1 THE PRODUCT DESIGN DATA IS PROVIDED BY THE COPYRIGHT HOLDERS AND 
CONTRIBUTORS "AS IS" AND ANY EXPRESS OR IMPLIED WARRANTIES, INCLUDING, BUT 
NOT LIMITED TO, THE IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A 
PARTICULAR PURPOSE ARE DISCLAIMED. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE COPYRIGHT OWNER OR 
CONTRIBUTORS BE LIABLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, 
EXEMPLARY, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES (INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, 
PROCUREMENT OF SUBSTITUTE GOODS OR SERVICES; LOSS OF USE, DATA, OR PROFITS; 
OR BUSINESS INTERRUPTION) HOWEVER CAUSED AND ON ANY THEORY OF LIABILITY, 
WHETHER IN CONTRACT, STRICT LIABILITY, OR TORT (INCLUDING NEGLIGENCE OR 
OTHERWISE) ARISING IN ANY WAY OUT OF THE USE OF THIS PRODUCT DESIGN DATA, 
EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGE.
